width="100%" border="0" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" role="presentation" style="padding-bottom:32px;text-align:center"><tbody><tr><td><img alt="YNOT London" height="36" src="https://staging.ynotlondon.com/brand/ynot-logo-black.png" style="display:inline-block;outline:none;border:none;text-decoration:none;height:auto;max-width:140px" width="140"/></td></tr></tbody></table><h2 style="font-family:Playfair Display, Georgia, serif;font-size:22px">About your return.</h2><p style="font-size:14px;line-height:24px;margin-top:16px;margin-bottom:16px">Hi Anna, thank you for sending back return RT-2026-00007 (from order YN-2026-00042). After inspecting it, we&#x27;re not able to issue a refund this time, and we wanted to explain why.</p><table align="center" width="100%" border="0" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" role="presentation" style="margin-top:24px"><tbody><tr><td><p style="font-size:12px;line-height:24px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.1em;color:#666;margin:0 0 8px;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0">Reason</p><p style="font-size:14px;line-height:24px;margin:0;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;margin-right:0">Item shows clear signs of wear beyond inspection.</p></td></tr></tbody></table><table align="center" width="100%" border="0" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" role="presentation" style="margin-top:24px"><tbody><tr><td><p style="font-size:12px;line-height:24px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.1em;color:#666;margin:0 0 8px;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0">Inspection notes</p><p style="font-size:14px;line-height:24px;margin:0;white-space:pre-wrap;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;margin-right:0">Tag missing; light scuffing on collar.</p></td></tr></tbody></table><hr style="width:100%;border:none;border-top:1px solid #eaeaea;border-color:#e5e5e5;margin:24px 0"/><table align="center" width="100%" border="0" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" role="presentation"><tbody><tr><td><p style="font-size:13px;line-height:24px;margin:0;color:#666;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;margin-right:0">If you&#x27;d like to discuss this further or have us return the items to you, please reply to this email or write to <a href="mailto:hello@ynotlondon.com?subject=Return%20RT-2026-00007" style="color:#111">hello@ynotlondon.com</a> — we read every message.</p></td></tr></tbody></table><hr style="width:100%;border:none;border-top:1px solid #eaeaea;border-color:#e5e5e5;margin:48px 0 24px"/><table align="center" width="100%" border="0" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" role="presentation"><tbody><tr><td><p style="font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;color:#666666;margin:0;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;margin-right:0">YNOT London · 13 Elvaston Place, Flat 1, London SW7 5QG ·<!-- --> <a href="https://staging.ynotlondon.com" style="color:#666666">staging.ynotlondon.com</a></p></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table><!--/$--></body></html>"`;
